snippet.title: Abyss Crew Release
snippet.description:
Abyss Crew is a multiplayer coop submarine videogame in a steampunk submarine.

Game has been released on 31. March:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/769520/Abyss_Crew

More information on :
https://www.abysscrew.com

Trailer creation : Alexis Caroff and Pol Grasland-Mongrain
Music : Flowing into the darkness (Nyoko) and The Complex (Kevin McLeod)
